response.overview: Where bounty hunters have failed, could a superheroine succeed? The Filipina Flamethrower, aspiring member of The Legion of Purity, has come to try her luck at the ultimate hero score, The Nameless Meta. So far, every ninja, bounty hunter, and would-be collector of the hundred million dollar bounty on his head has failed. Will her amazing suoerhuman strength and a pure heart make the difference? I think we all know the answer to that. And soon, so will helpless Jazmine, the Flamethrower herself, naked and hungry for his touch!
response.tagline: Where Bounty Hunters And Assassins Fail, Can A Superheroine Prevail?
response.title: The Filipina Flamethrower
